channel.title: Client wont let me log on
channel.description: Alright i have started back up a new rsps Its fully operation as far as i know. Runelocus's status check says its online. K well i copied the client and changed all ip's in client.java and gui.java to "127.0.0.1" and it says No response from server try another world." So i changed all to 0.0.0.0 and it said the same thing. If it helps im using the Teamtorva client and not sure what source as im only hosting the server for a friend. I think it is the team torva source edited a bit though so can someone help me?
